Package: femleadR
Title: Tools for Analyzing Female Leadership Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sophia", "Woodard", email = "smwoodar@calpoly.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Addison", "Weaver", email = "aweave10@calpoly.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Scarlet", "Kwan", email = "skwan02@calpoly.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides functions to streamline the analysis of how female world
    leaders impact GDP, unemployment, and other economic factors. Includes
    tools for generating relevant visualizations and summary tables, reducing
    repetitive code across analyses.
